OL,3,CTribute to 'kind soul' killed in hit-
OL,4,Cand-run as car still missing
OL,6,FThe family of an elderly cyclist
OL,7,Fkilled in a hit-and-run crash have
OL,8,Fdescribed him as a "kind soul" as
OL,9,Fpolice continue to search for the car
OL,10,Finvolved.
OL,12,FGraham Slinn, 81 was hit by a
OL,13,FVolkswagen Golf on the A57 at Todwick,
OL,14,FRotherham, on Friday, 4 April. He died
OL,15,Fat the scene, but the driver fled.
OL,17,FIn a statement, Mr Slinn's family
OL,18,Fdescribed him as a "kind soul".
