OL,3,CTribute to 'kind soul' killed in hit-
OL,4,Cand-run as car still missing
OL,6,FThey said: "He was always giving,
OL,7,Falways helping ` from mowing the
OL,8,Fneighbour's lawn to rescuing stray
OL,9,Fanimals, to lighting up a room with
OL,10,Fhis singing at karaoke.
OL,12,F"He was gentle. Funny. Kind to his
OL,13,Fcore. And now he's gone."
OL,15,FMr Slinn worked as a scaffolder,
OL,16,Fbefore becoming a carer for adults
OL,17,Fwith learning disabilities.
OL,19,FHe was due to celebrate his 60th
OL,20,Fwedding anniversary this year.
