OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police said the car,
OL,7,Fwhich had damage to its front bumper,
OL,8,Fpassenger side headlight and wing
OL,9,Fmirror, is still missing.
OL,11,FOfficers believe it drove off towards
OL,12,FKillamarsh following the collision.
OL,14,FMr Slinn's daughter appealed for
OL,15,Fpeople to come forward with
OL,16,Finformation.
OL,18,F"We just want justice because if
OL,19,Fsomeone could do this to my dad, they
OL,20,Fcould do it to yours too," she said.
